```json
{
  "application": "PyTorch",
  "details": {
    "framework": "PyTorch",
    "libraries": [
      "torch",
      "torch.distributed",
      "nccl"
    ],
    "resource_requirements": {
      "nodes": 2,
      "tasks_per_node": 1,
      "cpus_per_task": 96,
      "gpus_per_node": 8,
      "partition": "production-cluster",
      "slurm_gres": "gpu:8"
    },
    "environment_variables": {
      "CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES": "SLURM_STEP_GPUS",
      "MASTER_ADDR": "scontrol show hostnames $SLURM_JOB_NODELIST | head -n 1",
      "MASTER_PORT": "6000",
      "NCCL_ASYNC_ERROR_HANDLING": "1",
      "NCCL_PROTO": "simple",
      "RDMAV_FORK_SAFE": "1",
      "FI_EFA_FORK_SAFE": "1",
      "FI_EFA_USE_DEVICE_RDMA": "1",
      "FI_PROVIDER": "efa",
      "FI_LOG_LEVEL": "1",
      "NCCL_IB_DISABLE": "1",
      "NCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME": "ens"
    },
    "slurm_options": {
      "job_name": "laiona6plus-f8-vanilla-resblocks-ema",
      "output": "/admin/home/suraj/logs/maskgit-imagenet/%x-%j.out",
      "exclusive": true
    },
    "commands": [
      "source /admin/home/suraj/.bashrc",
      "source /fsx/suraj/miniconda3/etc/profile.d/conda.sh",
      "conda activate muse",
      "mkdir -p $OUTPUT_DIR",
      "touch $LOG_PATH",
      "pushd $MUSE_REPO",
      "srun $SRUN_ARGS --jobid $SLURM_JOB_ID bash -c \"$LAUNCHER --node_rank \$SLURM_PROCID --role \$SLURMD_NODENAME: $CMD\" 2>&1 | tee $LOG_PATH"
    ]
  }
}
```
